      <guid>https://rbroc.github.io/about/</guid>
      <description>I am a tenure-track Assistant Professor at the Department of Culture, Cognition and Computation @ Aarhus University. Previously, I was a postdoc at Psychoinformatics Lab @ UT Austin.
My work focuses on NLP and data science methods, applied to the study of clinical conditions, cognitive processes and individual differences, and social and political phenomena. I spend most of my time developing research methods, trying to make ML tools and practices more available to research communities in cognitive and social sciences, and writing scientific papers about it.</description>
